insights: Multiple recipe versions exist for the same meal with slight cost and nutritional variations
Chicken & Mushroom Marsala has 6 versions but all marked 'Graveyard' status (discontinued/inactive)

Meals are categorized by multiple dietary attributes: Keto, Calorie Smart, High Protein, Dairy Free, etc.
Protein types are primary differentiator: Chicken Breast, Beef Shredded, Salmon Filet, Turkey Sliced
Cuisine types span European (Italian, Greek), Asian (Korean, Chinese), and North American (Southwestern, Midwestern)
Container types and sleeve colors indicate operational/packaging requirements
Comprehensive nutritional tracking includes calories, sodium, fat, carbs, protein, and fiber
Cost management shows actual cost vs. max meal cost for profitability tracking
Preparation methods are detailed (Marinade, Grill, Oven, Braiser) for kitchen operations
